• Breath of heaven • 🕊️ 

Thank you @chantar for capturing my soft side. 📷
Thanking the Lord! ✨

• Renovation Station • ✨

📷 @oshenstudio

• The Best is Yet to Come • 🧶

Had such a fun time creating my styling studio that eventually turned into my extended closet. About 6 years ago I went through a series of hardships that led to me nearly selling off all my possessions and fashion to put food on the table. It’s been such a healing experience to be able to express myself again through wardrobe and tap into my external expression. So much has been restored & multiplied. 

Home has become another extension of my personality, and combining some of my favorite things (interior & style) has been a gratifying experience. Grateful is an understatement. ✨

📷 @oshenstudio

“Naked came I out of my mother's womb, and naked shall I return thither: the Lord gave, and the Lord hath taken away; blessed be the name of the Lord.”

Job 1:21

📷 @oshenstudio
• People hate to see you happy. Keep on smiling. Keep on rising. Keep on shining. • 🙏🏾

• Unshakeable• 💪🏾 #TB 

Always a pleasure to sport @menagerieintimates @theboyworelace by my talented friend @romansipe. 

Photographed by the precise @oshenstudio 📷
• People love to point out your flaws & laugh at your past. Thankfully, I embrace mine. •
• When you begin healing & start stepping into your higher self, you will begin to look unrecognizable to the people who only knew you by your trauma & pain. •
• Healing looks good on me. Very thankful. ✨

• Baptize Me • 🌊 

A big thank you to those who’ve stuck with me over the years. I’ve taken some time away to heal, restore, and prepare for the next phase of my life. I’m relieved and excited for what’s to come in the future. I’ve been planning, working, writing, and conceptualizing behind the scenes on a project for the last couple of years, on a big dream of mine since I was a child. I hope to see that dream manifest in the upcoming year, and finally put all the pieces to this creative puzzle together. 

I appreciate all of the support for this unconventional path I’ve taken in expressing myself over the years. I promise I won’t leave it behind. 

Love Colin. 🤍

📷 @oshenstudio
